(505, 3292, 'cs_job_desc', '<p>Looking for someone to buy a fully functional &nbsp;SaaS app.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700\">What does it do?</span><br>Professionally built SaaS app, with a beautiful marketing site.&nbsp;<br><br>Growbeam is a modern cloud-based applicant tracking system that allows you to easily track and manage your hiring process all in one place. Post job openings, source and manage candidates and use analytics to make good hiring decisions with your team.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700\">Check out the marketing website and then ask me any questions:</span></p><p><a href=\"http://growbeam.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://growbeam.com</a><br><br>This is a fully functional product that needs someone to take it to the next level with investing some time in marketing and sales.</p><p>Please contact me if you are serious about this and I will be happy to run you through a demo of the product and answer any questions you may have.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700\">Features</span></p><ul><li>Customised hiring stages for each department</li><li>Organise phone screens &amp; interviews using the in built two-way email sync.</li><li>Customized hiring teams/committees</li><li>Resumes and cover letters are automatically scanned and turned into rich candidate profiles.</li><li>Hiring team/committee automatically notified by changes to a candidate</li><li>Analytics on everything</li><li>Beautiful marketing site</li><li>Create careers site, or just embed application form</li><li>Short share code (http://grbm.co)</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>SKILLS &amp; REQUIREMENTS</h3><p>You are:</p><ul><li>Serious about purchasing a fully functional product</li><li>An entrepreneur, marketeer, developer or sales person looking for a could opportunity</li></ul>'),
